OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRemaining
OL,6,Flargely cloudy through the evening and
OL,7,Fearly hours, with rain which could be
OL,8,Fheavy at times. Towards dawn rain will
OL,9,Fstart to ease, but remaining mostly
OL,10,Fcloudy. Breezy near coasts.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FLingering rain clearing and
OL,13,Fcloud thinning Saturday morning,
OL,14,Fbefore a band of showers progresses
OL,15,Feastward in the afternoon. Skies
OL,16,Fclearing later, then further light
OL,17,Frain overnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
