OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FStrong
OL,6,Fwinds Sunday and Monday, with some
OL,7,Frain spreading east but also some
OL,8,Fdrier spells. Likely dry Tuesday with
OL,9,Flight winds and sunny spells.
OL,10,FTemperatures a little above average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
